# Cyber-Noir UI Transformation Plan

Transform the dashboard into a premium "Cyber-Noir Command Center" with advanced styling and animations.

## Proposed Changes

### [Global Styles & Aesthetic]

#### [MODIFY] [index.css](file:///c:/Users/G/Desktop/checkDigitalsecurity/src/index.css)
- Implement background `#020617` with animated SVG grid.
- Add fixed scanline overlay.
- Define glassmorphism utility classes with cyan borders (`#22d3ee`).
- Add animations: glitch effect, pulse for icons, and hover glow/scale.
- Set global font to 'JetBrains Mono' (importing from Google Fonts).

### [Main Application Component]

#### [MODIFY] [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/G/Desktop/checkDigitalsecurity/src/App.jsx)
- Update layout to incorporate new background and scanlines.
- Implement Framer Motion stagger animations for module entry.
- Ensure all headers have the hover glitch effect.

### [Module Components]

#### [MODIFY] all modules
- Ensure `useState`, `useEffect`, `useRef` are imported from 'react'.
- Apply `glass-card` class and ensure icons use pulse animation for alerts.

#### [MODIFY] [SocialBot.jsx](file:///c:/Users/G/Desktop/checkDigitalsecurity/src/components/modules/SocialBot.jsx)
- Switch from manual `chatEndRef.scrollTo` to `scrollIntoView()` for reliability and to prevent crashes.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm run lint` to check for import/variable issues.

### Manual Verification
- Visual inspection of the "Cyber-Noir" theme (grid, scanlines, glassmorphism).
- Test hover effects (scale, glow, glitch).
- Verify "Social Bot" chat auto-scrolls correctly without errors.
- Check staggered entrance animations on page load.
